snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK Vol. 4 The Ride Trailer
snippet.description: Play the game that many consider to be YDKJ's most fun offering -- The Ride! Already played it? Trust us, you've forgotten everything by now. For the fourth volume of the mega-award-winning CD-ROM trivia game show, the YOU DON'T KNOW JACK crew decided to throw out the YDKJ rule book and start fresh!
